```

### Code Quality Tools
```bash
# Run linting
ruff check .

# Run type checking
mypy slack_blocksmith/

# Run tests
pytest

# Run tests with coverage
pytest --cov=slack_blocksmith --cov-report=html

# Format code
ruff format .
```

